# SSGPT6 – UI Foundation

This repo contains the **front-end only** foundation for the SSGPT6 platform:

- Membership funnel (free play → lockout → subscription)
- Admin suite (dashboard, analytics, logs, content, AI tools)
- Central control hubs (multi-page + single-page)
- All logic is **UI-only**. No real payments, no real auth, no external APIs.

## Structure

- `index-membership.html` – Email capture + free play entry
- `free-play.html` – 10-minute free session (timer)
- `free-play-lockout.html` – Session ended → membership prompt
- `subscription.html` – Membership completion UI
- `admin-*.html` – Admin tools (dashboard, analytics, logs, content, AI tools)
- `ssgpt6-*.html` – Central control hubs
- `central-activation-hub.html` – One-click module activation (UI log only)
- `styles.css` – Shared styling

## Safety

- No real payments
- No real authentication
- No account access
- All “activation” is visual only

Backend, payments, and auth must be implemented separately with proper security and legal review.
